title: Supreme Court orders probe on the use of spy software
description:
A Supreme Court ordered Congress to present within ten days its flight plan to regulate the use of spy software by government agencies.  The move comes a week after the Federal Police started to raid addresses linked to current and former officials within the Brazilian Intelligence Agency (Abin) accused of illegally accessing geolocalization data of […]
